Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:03.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}向邪惡揮舞復仇之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:07.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}為善良賜予救濟之死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:10.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}我這汙穢的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:14.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}究竟會斬向何方
